data.description: Welcome to ''Golf Resort'' Style Living! Home is located steps away from a beautiful pond and is on the golf course. Take a short walk to Golden Hills Park. Major freeways, shopping, restaurants and hospitals are only a few miles away. No HOA monthly fees! Charming home has been redesigned with a ''Guest Retreat'' with separate private access to property with a large walk-in closet, updated tiled shower with plenty of storage space and your own kitchenette. Large backyard and patio to enjoy the breathtaking Arizona sunset views. Home welcomes you into a spacious kitchen with island, large windows for natural lighting and views to the 19th hole ''Arizona Golf Course''. Home  offers Value, Comfort, and Possibilities. Why wait, Call today! New lighting fixtures and ceilings fans throughout home, updated tile shower and luxury plank flooring in kitchen and hallways, newer roof, newly painted interior with neutral tones, wood burning fireplace and extra space for entertaining. Create your own oasis with plenty of room for a pool or spa in the backyard. How about the "Guest Retreat" this calls for the perfect place for temporary roomates. Take advantage and call today! This is a one of a kind with amazing views, value and opportunity!
